{
  "id": "adv_event_2408_01_01",
  "title": "リベンジ\n大作戦",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "嘘のスケジュールを知らされたとも知らず\n一人、楽屋にやって来たfranちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unaware that she was given a fake schedule‚\nfran-chan came to the dressing room alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.5869613647000005,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9633.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "これから恐ろしいことが待ち受けているとも知らず\nのんびりスマホをチェックしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not knowing that something terrifying awaits her\nshe's leisurely checking her phone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "endTime": 13.3062129974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "んー、今日のニュースは……ふむふむ\n総理は昨日の記者会見で、金融緩和について……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ today's news is… I see‚ I see.\nThe Prime Minister talked about monetary easing at yesterday's press conference…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5,
      "endTime": 23.810000228899998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "さすがfranちゃん\n政治経済のニュースチェックも欠かしませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of fran-chan.\nShe never fails to check political and economic news.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "endTime": 29.9510882378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 30.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、kanaとmihoってば遅いわね\n遅れるって連絡もなかったのに、何かあったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ kana and miho are late.\nThey didn't even let me know they'd be late‚ I wonder if something happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1666666667,
      "endTime": 38.6272787731,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14463.333333300003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "franちゃん、心配してくれてありがと～\nでも人の心配だけじゃなくて、自分の心配もしないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-chan‚ thanks for worrying about us~\nBut you should worry about yourself‚ not just others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8333333333,
      "endTime": 48.0845347722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ではでは、franちゃんをじっくりじっくり\nコワ～い世界に誘っていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's slowly‚ carefully\nlure fran-chan into a scary~ world.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3,
      "endTime": 56.233106708499996,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ball-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15260.000000000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 56.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "お？　机に置いてあったペットボトルが\n勝手にかたかたと動き出して……あ、ごとっと落ちた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? The plastic bottle on the table\nstarted rattling on its own… ah‚ it fell with a thud!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333333333,
      "endTime": 65.6510655721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 65.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　……まぁ、別にいいか\n経済ジャーナリストによれば、景気は短期的には……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hm? …Well‚ whatever.\nAccording to economic journalists‚ the economy in the short term…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8666666667,
      "endTime": 76.3435827891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "franちゃん、ニュースに集中し過ぎて、ひとりでに\n机のペットボトルが落ちたのに気付いてませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-chan is too focused on the news to notice\nthat the plastic bottle fell off the desk by itself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5333333333,
      "endTime": 84.07809527709999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_noise-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13633.333333399989
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "さぁて、お次はですね～……\nmihoちゃん、耳栓どこ……うぎゃっ、凄い音！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ next is…\nmiho-chan‚ where are the earplugs… gyah‚ what a loud sound!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2666666667,
      "endTime": 92.4690706889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 92.5666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ、びっくりした。……テレビの故障？\nいきなりマックスで鳴らないでほしいわ、うー耳が痛い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ that startled me. …Is the TV broken?\nI wish it wouldn't suddenly blast at maximum volume‚ ugh my ears hurt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5666651408,
      "endTime": 103.2877762477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4999984741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に点いたりして、なんなのかしら……\n勘弁してよね、もう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It turned on by itself‚ what's going on…\nGive me a break‚ seriously…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4999984741,
      "endTime": 110.1396581649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "お？　だんだん嫌な予感がしてきたようですね\nまだまだいきますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? It seems she's starting to get a bad feeling.\nWe're just getting started~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7000005086,
      "endTime": 117.2828805287,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6633.334859300006
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 117.466671753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　また何か聞こえてきた！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? I hear something again!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.466671753,
      "endTime": 120.8074201108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 121.0000050863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うふふふ、ふふ……うふふふふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ufufufu‚ fufu… ufufufufufu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0000050863,
      "endTime": 128.9333399456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "憎い……全ての人間が憎い……滅べ、滅んでしまえ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hate them… I hate all humans… Perish. Just perish already…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9333399456,
      "endTime": 138.17999757130002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "え、何。……なんなのよ、この声！　そう言えば\nkanaが、この楽屋に幽霊が出るとかなんとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What‚ what is this. …What is this voice! Come to think of it\nkana said something about ghosts appearing in this dressing room…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3666641236,
      "endTime": 147.66255950930002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8666641236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "これが、その……幽霊、ってやつ……？\n私、そんな祟られるような悪いことしてないわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is… that… a ghost…?\nI haven't done anything bad to be cursed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8666641236,
      "endTime": 155.4889998437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 155.6999974569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "たまに事務所のトイレ掃除だってやってるし\nむしろ、いいことしてるのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even clean the office toilets sometimes\nI'm doing good things instead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6999974569,
      "endTime": 160.1965282759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "ならトイレ掃除の神様が助けてくれたって良くない！？\nここで呪われたら、一生恨んでやる！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then shouldn't the toilet cleaning god help me!?\nIf I get cursed here‚ I'll resent it forever!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.3999974569,
      "endTime": 167.4179792722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 167.6333307903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "トイレ掃除くらいで、幽霊追い払ってもらおうってのは\nちょっと図々しいと思うよ、franちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really think cleaning toilets is enough to chase away ghosts?\nThat’s a bit much‚ fran-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6333307903,
      "endTime": 175.1559612911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "さてさて、最後の大仕掛け！！\nいっけ～～！　幽霊とご対面で～す！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then‚ time for the grand finale!!\nHere we go~! Time to meet the ghost~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3666641236,
      "endTime": 183.02782058719998,
