      "text": "{user}さんは渋ってるけど……\nま、当然よね。私達の実態なんて絶対お出し出来ないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san seems reluctant though…\nWell‚ of course. There's no way we can show our true selves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 354.6665847778,
      "endTime": 363.9088521957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
