      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "でも……そうねぇ\nふふっ、いいこと思いついたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… let's see.\nFufu‚ I have a good idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 364.0999181111,
      "endTime": 370.5939998944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor024.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nちょっとお話があるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san\nI have something to discuss with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 372.8999181111,
      "endTime": 376.2311199505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（なんだろう、franさんから話があるというだけで）\n（すでに嫌な予感がする……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder what it is‚ just the fact that fran-san wants to talk）\n（already gives me a bad feeling…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.4332514445,
      "endTime": 381.8379453342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor025.m4a",
      "text": "さっき制作会社の人と話してるのを聞いちゃったん\nですが、スリクスの密着取材の話、受けてみませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I overheard you talking with the production company earlier.\nHow about we accept the ⅢX close coverage proposal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 382.0332514445,
      "endTime": 390.0298275629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor026.m4a",
      "text": "密着取材って言っても、カメラが入るのは\nあくまでスタジオとか舞台袖とか、楽屋でしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it's close coverage‚ cameras would only be in\nstudios‚ backstage‚ dressing rooms and such.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 390.2332514445,
      "endTime": 396.66649405159995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor027.m4a",
      "text": "そこで私達の素を見せなければいいんだから\nいつもとやることは大して変わりませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As long as we don't show our true selves there\nwhat we do won't be much different from usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 396.8665847778,
      "endTime": 402.6296685218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうですけど、いつもはそういうの嫌がるのに\n今回に限って、何か理由でも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ but you usually dislike that sort of thing.\nIs there some reason this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 402.8332514445,
      "endTime": 410.2358820597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor028.m4a",
      "text": "べっつにー、ただ頑張って仕事しようってだけですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really~ I just want to work hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 410.4332514445,
      "endTime": 415.4165619532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor029.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん。あいつらだって\n少しは、カメラの前でみっともないとこ晒せばいいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heh. They should have to\nshow their embarrassing sides on camera too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 415.5999181111,
      "endTime": 421.95293382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-kor030.m4a",
      "text": "あ、kanaとmihoには私から言っておくので\n{user}さんは黙ってて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I'll tell kana and miho myself\nso please don't say anything‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 422.1665847778,
      "endTime": 427.8794194221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（絶対に、何かマズいことを考えてる……！）\n（俺に出来ることはなんだ……とりあえず、胃薬の準備か）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's definitely planning something bad…!）\n（What can I do… I guess I’ll go grab some stomach medicine.）",
        "id": ""
